      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cequin macehualmeh tlen motechtiah ceyoc ininaxca, huan quintlanahnahuatiah, ni hueliz pampa quinitzquihqueh, zo quincouhqueh quemman tlacatqueh.</Note_Text>
